message: "If you use this software, please cite it as below."
title: "autoguardrails: an autoresearch-style guardrail policy loop"
abstract: >-
  An LLM / AI-safety guardrail research library and evaluation harness
  (autoresearch-style): it searches over a single mutable policy.md surface to
  minimize attack success rate (ASR) against a fixed evaluation suite, with a
  benign-pass floor.
type: software
authors:
